    "name": "Shadow Mastiff",
    "type": "alien",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Native to dimly lit areas of the Shadow Plane, these ferocious and alien-yet-familiar beasts often inspire a primal terror in those who witness them in drug-fueled nightmares and visions of that dimension.<br/><br/> Though they are commonly known as shadow mastiffs, these creatures have little in common with actual canines except for their appearance, and shadow mastiffs encountered outside of the Pact Worlds might bear a closer resemblance to local predatory beasts. Shadow mastiffs discover new hunting grounds when power-hungry or corrupt mortals summon them, or when mystical and technomagical rituals tear the veil that separates their world from the Material Plane."
        }
    ],
